datasets.name: 0aefb68d
queryLines:
SELECT company, job_title, job_field, salary_low, salary_high
FROM dev.job_prospects.job_1900_silver_inferred
ORDER BY salary_high DESC
LIMIT 10;

datasets.name: 035939b3
queryLines:
SELECT job_field, AVG(salary_high) as average_salary_high
FROM dev.job_prospects.job_1900_silver
GROUP BY job_field
ORDER BY average_salary_high DESC

datasets.name: 2aa99fc8
queryLines:
SELECT
  'Job Counts by Field' AS metric,
  job_field,
  count AS value
FROM
  `dev`.`job_prospects`.`fct_top_10_last_month`
WHERE
  job_field IS NOT NULL
UNION ALL
SELECT
  'Average Salary & Experience by Field' AS metric,
  job_field,
  avg_salary AS value
FROM
  `dev`.`job_prospects`.`fct_avg_salary_exp`
WHERE
  job_field IS NOT NULL
UNION ALL
SELECT
  'Average Experience by Field' AS metric,
  job_field,
  avg_experience AS value
FROM
  `dev`.`job_prospects`.`fct_avg_salary_exp`
WHERE
  job_field IS NOT NULL
UNION ALL
SELECT
  'Job Views by Field' AS metric,
  job_field,
  view_count AS value
FROM
  `dev`.`job_prospects`.`fct_jobs_by_views`
WHERE
  job_field IS NOT NULL
UNION ALL
SELECT
  'Top Job Fields Last Week' AS metric,
  job_field,
  count AS value
FROM
  `dev`.`job_prospects`.`fct_top_10_last_week`
WHERE
  job_field IS NOT NULL
UNION ALL
SELECT
  'Job Counts by Area' AS metric,
  area,
  count AS value
FROM
  `dev`.`job_prospects`.`fct_jobs_by_area`
WHERE
  area IS NOT NULL
UNION ALL
SELECT
  'Job Counts by Department' AS metric,
  job_department,
  count AS value
FROM
  `dev`.`job_prospects`.`fct_jobs_by_department`
WHERE
  job_department IS NOT NULL
ORDER BY
  metric,
  value DESC;
